## 🎨 Analisis Design System & Frontend Best Practices

### Design Tokens yang Sudah Digunakan (HARUS Konsisten)

Berdasarkan analisis [dashboard/page.tsx](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/app/dashboard/page.tsx), [admin/page.tsx](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/app/admin/page.tsx), dan [questions/page.tsx](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/app/admin/questions/page.tsx):

```
Background       : bg-slate-950 (utama), bg-slate-900/50 (card)
Card Border      : border-slate-800, border-2
Card Radius      : rounded-3xl atau rounded-[2.5rem]
Heading          : text-4xl font-black tracking-tight
Subheading       : text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest
Table Header     : text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500
Icon Library     : lucide-react (BUKAN heroicons atau font-awesome)
Primary Color    : indigo-600/500 (buttons, active states)
Badge Style      : rounded-xl, bg-{color}-500/10, text-{color}-400, border-none
Button Style     : rounded-2xl, py-6, font-bold, shadow-xl shadow-indigo-600/20
Pagination       : rounded-xl, bg-indigo-600 active page
Animation        : animate-pulse (skeleton), animate-in slide-in / fade-in / zoom-in
Empty State      : Icon besar (w-12 h-12 text-slate-800) + teks uppercase tracking-widest
```

### Pola Frontend yang HARUS Diikuti (Best Practice)

| Pattern | Detail | Referensi |
|---|---|---|
| **Data Fetching** | [fetch()](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/app/admin/questions/page.tsx#46-58) dengan `credentials: 'include'` (HTTP-only cookie) | AuthContext pattern |
| **Loading State** | Skeleton pulses bukan spinner (kecuali full-page) | Questions page |
| **Pagination** | Server-side, `page` + `size` params, response `{items, total, page, size}` | admin_questions.py |
| **Filter Bar** | Di dalam Card rounded-[2rem] di atas tabel | Questions page |
| **Table** | Dalam div `rounded-[2.5rem]` dengan overflow-hidden | Questions page |
| **Actions Column** | Icon buttons: Edit, Delete, MoreVertical | Questions page |
| **Modal** | Fixed overlay + backdrop-blur + Card zoom-in animation | Import modal |
| **Toast/Message** | Inline alert di atas konten, bisa di-dismiss | Questions page |
| **Empty State** | Centered icon + text di dalam tabel | Questions page |

### Rekomendasi Tambahan Best Practice

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Reusable Components** — Saat ini banyak pattern yang di-copy-paste (tabel, pagination, filter, modal). Sebaiknya buat komponen reusable:

1. **`AdminDataTable`** — Komponen tabel reusable dengan sorting, skeleton loading, empty state
2. **`AdminPagination`** — Komponen pagination terpisah  
3. **`AdminFilterBar`** — Search + filter dropdown container
4. **`ConfirmModal`** — Modal konfirmasi delete dengan danger styling
5. **`AdminPageHeader`** — Header standar (title + subtitle + action buttons)

> [!TIP]
> **Charting Library** — Untuk analytics, gunakan **Recharts** (React-native, ringan, support dark theme). Alternative: **Chart.js** via react-chartjs-2.

---

## 📋 Proposed Changes

### Component 1: Reusable Admin Components (Frontend)

#### [NEW] [AdminDataTable.tsx](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/components/admin/AdminDataTable.tsx)
- Generic table component dengan props: `columns`, `data`, `loading`, `emptyIcon`, `emptyText`
- Built-in skeleton loading (5 rows animate-pulse)
- Hover row highlight `hover:bg-slate-900/30`

#### [NEW] [AdminPagination.tsx](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/components/admin/AdminPagination.tsx)
- Props: `page`, `total`, `pageSize`, `onPageChange`
- Menampilkan "Showing X to Y of Z" + prev/next buttons

#### [NEW] [AdminPageHeader.tsx](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/components/admin/AdminPageHeader.tsx)
- Props: `title`, `subtitle`, `actions` (React nodes for buttons)

#### [NEW] [ConfirmModal.tsx](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/components/admin/ConfirmModal.tsx)
- Props: `isOpen`, `onClose`, `onConfirm`, `title`, `description`, `variant: 'danger' | 'warning'`
- Backdrop blur + zoom-in animation (consistent with import modal pattern)

