### Component 2: `/admin/packages` — Paket Ujian

#### Backend

#### [MODIFY] [admin_packages.py](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/backend/api/v1/endpoints/admin_packages.py)
- **Tambah `PUT /{package_id}`** untuk update package (title, description, price, is_premium, category)
- **Tambah pagination** pada GET `/` → response `{items, total, page, size}` (sama seperti questions)
- **Tambah field `question_count`** di response list (via subquery count)
- **Tambah field `transaction_count`** di response list

#### Frontend

#### [NEW] [packages/page.tsx](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/app/admin/packages/page.tsx)
- **Tampilan:** Tabel/Grid view dengan kolom: Title, Category (badge TWK/TIU/TKP/Mix), Price (formatted Rp), Premium (badge), Jumlah Soal, Aksi
- **Fitur:** 
  - Filter by category (TWK/TIU/TKP/Mix/Semua)
  - Search by title
  - Create modal (form: title, description, price, category, is_premium toggle)
  - Edit modal (pre-filled form)
  - Delete with confirmation modal
- **UI:** Mengikuti pattern Questions page — tabel di dalam rounded card + pagination

---

### Component 3: `/admin/users` — Pengguna

#### Backend

#### [NEW] [admin_users.py](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/backend/api/v1/endpoints/admin_users.py)
- **`GET /admin/users`** — List users dengan pagination + search (by email/name) + filter (role, is_active)
  - Join `users` + `user_profiles` untuk full_name & target_instansi
  - Response: `{items: [{id, email, role, is_active, created_at, full_name, target_instansi, total_sessions, total_transactions}], total, page, size}`
- **`GET /admin/users/{user_id}`** — Detail user tunggal (profile + exam history + transactions)
- **`PUT /admin/users/{user_id}`** — Update role, is_active (ban/unban)
- **`DELETE /admin/users/{user_id}`** — Soft delete / deactivate

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/backend/main.py) — Register router baru

#### Frontend

#### [NEW] [users/page.tsx](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/app/admin/users/page.tsx)
- **Tampilan:** Tabel dengan kolom: Avatar (initial), Email, Nama Lengkap, Role (badge admin/participant), Status (badge active/banned), Registered, Total Sesi, Aksi
- **Fitur:**
  - Search by email/nama
  - Filter by role (admin/participant/semua) + status (active/inactive)
  - Inline toggle untuk activate/deactivate user
  - View detail modal (riwayat ujian + transaksi user)
  - Change role dropdown
- **UI:** Tabel pattern sama seperti questions, avatar menggunakan initial circle (consistent dengan leaderboard)

---

### Component 4: `/admin/analytics` — Analitik

#### Backend

#### [NEW] [admin_analytics.py](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/backend/api/v1/endpoints/admin_analytics.py)
- **`GET /admin/analytics/overview`** — Aggregated stats:
  - Total users, total questions, total packages, total transactions (success), total revenue
  - Users registered today/this week/this month
  - Exam sessions today/this week/this month
- **`GET /admin/analytics/exam-stats`** — Exam performance stats:
  - Average scores (TWK, TIU, TKP, Total)
  - Pass rate percentage
  - Score distribution histogram data (buckets: 0-100, 101-200, 201-300, 301-400, 401-500, 501-575)
- **`GET /admin/analytics/revenue`** — Revenue analytics:
  - Daily/weekly/monthly revenue trend data (for chart)
  - Transaction count trend
  - Top selling packages
- **`GET /admin/analytics/user-growth`** — User registration trend (daily/monthly)

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/backend/main.py) — Register router baru

#### Frontend

#### [NEW] [analytics/page.tsx](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/app/admin/analytics/page.tsx)
- **Layout:** Dashboard-style grid layout
  - **Row 1:** Stats cards (Total Users, Total Revenue, Avg Score, Pass Rate) — gunakan pattern dari admin overview
  - **Row 2:** Charts area (2 columns)
    - Left: **Line Chart** — User registrations over time / Exam sessions trend
    - Right: **Bar Chart** — Score distribution (histogram)
  - **Row 3:** 
    - Left: **Area Chart** — Revenue trend
    - Right: **Table** — Top selling packages
- **Library:** Install `recharts` untuk charting
- **Fitur:** Date range filter (7 hari, 30 hari, 90 hari, custom)

---

### Component 5: `/admin/transactions` — Transaksi

#### Backend

#### [NEW] [admin_transactions.py](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/backend/api/v1/endpoints/admin_transactions.py)
- **`GET /admin/transactions`** — List transactions dengan pagination + filter:
  - Filter: `payment_status` (pending/success/failed), date range, package_id
  - Search: by user email
  - Join `users` + [packages](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/backend/api/v1/endpoints/admin_packages.py#31-38) untuk menampilkan email + package title
  - Response: `{items: [{id, user_email, package_title, amount, payment_status, snap_token, created_at, access_expires_at}], total, page, size}`
- **`GET /admin/transactions/summary`** — Aggregated: total revenue, count by status, daily trend
- **`PUT /admin/transactions/{transaction_id}/status`** — Manual override status (admin only, untuk kasus edge)

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/backend/main.py) — Register router baru

#### Frontend

#### [NEW] [transactions/page.tsx](file:///d:/ProjectAI/Test-CPNS/frontend/src/app/admin/transactions/page.tsx)
- **Tampilan:** Tabel dengan kolom: ID (short), User Email, Paket, Amount (Rp formatted), Status (badge colored: pending=yellow, success=green, failed=red), Tanggal, Aksi
- **Fitur:**
  - Search by email
  - Filter: status (pending/success/failed/semua), date range picker
  - Summary cards di atas tabel: Total Revenue, Jumlah Sukses, Jumlah Pending, Jumlah Gagal
  - Export CSV (optional nice-to-have)
  - Detail modal (snap_token, timestamps, user info)

